casebody.data:
Wednesday, March 24, 1999

MOTION DOCKET

99-542. White v. Konteh.

Trumbull App. No. 99-T-0020. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Trumbull County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of judgment of the Eleventh District Court of Appeals,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, granted.

Pfeifer, J., dissents. Resnick, J., not participating.
